                    "Description" : {
                        "Id" : "outcome_1_0",
                        "Name" : "Fast talk",
                        "Details" : "\"You're talking to the wrong person, friend,\" you say to the leader of the group. \"[[TGT_MW,{TGT_MW.Callsign}]] still works for me, so you can all get lost.\"\r\n\r\nThe leader looks at you, and his eyes widen. \"Ah, the Syndicate wants their money, and {TGT_MW.Firstname} owes them\u2014\"\r\n\r\nYou jab a finger at his chest. \"Wrong! {TGT_MW.SUBJ_C} no longer {TGT_MW.Gender?NonBinary:owe|Default:owes} you anything. We have a deal with <i>Front Man</i> and the Syndicate will have to just wait,\" you say. \"Now get out of my way. I'm busy.\"\r\n\r\nThe leader looks at you, \"You know <i>Front Man</i>?\"  He then drops his gaze and steps aside. You and {TGT_MW.Callsign} move on before he can reconsider. On the flight back to the <i>Argo</i>, {TGT_MW.Subj} {TGT_MW.Gender?NonBinary:talk|Default:talks} to you about {TGT_MW.DET} past\u2014a rare event for such a secretive MechWarrior.",
